bb{AOL})$ generated by the horizontal sums of nontrivial orthomodular\nlattices with nontrivial antiortholattices w.r.t. $\\mathbb{PBZL}^{\\ast }$, as\nwell as a relative axiomatization of the join of varieties $\\mathbb{OML}\\vee\nV(\\mathbb{AOL})$ w.r.t. $V(\\mathbb{OML}\\boxplus \\mathbb{AOL})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Nov 2018 17:35:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Dec 2018 16:24:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-13"}
