mission, supporting the scenario in which a\nLLAGN/LINER-like source is hidden in the centre of NGC4303. Thus, our results\nreveal a rather complex star formation history in NGC4303, with different\nstellar population components coexisting with a low efficiency accreting black\nhole in its centre.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Nov 2018 17:47:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
