ow/moderate volume fraction, and\nfails in the case of a fully dense suspension.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2018 11:07:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2018 17:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 May 2019 10:04:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-24"}
