d to reveal structure\ncomponents of neuronal circuits, and provide a powerful model for neural system\nidentification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2018 11:20:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2020 11:49:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
